Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.22,0:01:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.52,0:01:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.25,0:01:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.27,0:01:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.97,0:02:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Nameless Dragon Timaeus"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I looked at this palette, I confirmed my theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you are the only one who can solve the current crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and save mankind from their coming downfall of destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mankind's downfall of destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly do you mean by that, Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.43,0:02:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been recently studying the origin of Duel Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's much to tell from what I've found in the Ancient Egyptian tablets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High officials used spells to seal wicked spirits within stone tablets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to understand that these high officials
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.08,0:02:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,called the spirits from the stone tablets in order to protect themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.82,0:02:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are those... Dark Games?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.12,0:03:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These wicked spirits grew stronger until eventually they emerged from the stone tablets,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and evil power was created as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of this, an unbelievably tremendous power was born that threatened to destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nameless Pharaoh was the one who brought this evil power under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something like that happened in my other self's past...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was a long time ago, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it related to what's going on right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recently joined a research team while in America and may have discovered a lost civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I saw that in the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.76,0:03:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I myself closely examined the carvings resting there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what I found was... far beyond what I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at these.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those engraved markings we found suggest that Duel Monsters existed long before Ancient Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.96,0:04:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10,000 years ago, to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10,000 years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's really true, your discovery could completely rewrite history!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This stone tablet is quite the find.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monsters appear to be attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those engravings depict the part of my theory that suggests the Monsters tried to destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monsters did...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means the Monsters we saw recently are also trying to destroy the world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The omen has begun~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soon this world's gonna be destroyed~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what Haga-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Ryuzaki-{\i1}kun{\i0} were taking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.31,0:04:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10,000 years ago, as shown on these palettes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3,000 years ago in Egypt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the current situation just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all just a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.68,0:05:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.22,0:05:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Monsters is just a game created by Pegasus, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone must be playing a trick with the Monsters using the Duel Disks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} said his Solid Vision System wasn't the cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu, you're not gonna try and tell me Monsters are real, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.10,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monsters {\i1}are{\i0} real.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are depicted within ancient drawings...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.51,0:05:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The many gods, rituals, magic and spells are examples
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of human being's desires to awaken the Monsters from a different world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are trying to use this power for the sole purpose of proving their existence, or so I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you insult Grandpa's theory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus himself got his inspiration to create Duel Monsters after viewing the ancient stone carvings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, Rebeca.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I myself feel it's all a bit far fetched.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you, Professor Hopkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dark Games we fought with Malik in Battle City...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the God Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After being attacked by Ra, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't just Solid Vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.00,0:06:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And others besides the chosen ones were able to use the God Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a\N world that we're unaware of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Duel Monsters world...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, there's many theories relating to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Theses stating there may be other worlds other than our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time, space, different dimensions...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.72,0:06:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Entirely different worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some think there's\N even parallel universes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have quite the vocabulary\N for a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a {\i1}university student{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,University?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This child is something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I'm a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tensaiyo{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-e-n-s-a-i!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brat ain't cute at all...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0} did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down now, Rebeca.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not acting like a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely, what happened back in Ancient Egypt as well as now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has something to do with the Duel Monsters that almost destroyed the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one knows for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something only the nameless Pharaoh can tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.13,0:07:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you appeared in our era?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning to your rebirth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, those "Musketeers of Doma" said something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the forbidden door is opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the light of Orichalcos shall punish this sinful world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.62,0:07:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are the Musketeers of Doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just who are those guys...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, there's something else I'd like you to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, what is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who attacked us yesterday was wearing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looks just like it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just like a similar stone\N in the ancient ruins...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I study this for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm heading back to America in order to further investigate these ancient ruins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I find something out, I'll contact you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.93,0:08:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take Arthur and Rebeca to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe all this happened to the other me in his past...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah, but I don't remember any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:06.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.06,0:09:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What's wrong, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard someone say "help" just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.17,0:09:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you're just tired, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.07,0:09:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm headed home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop wondering about everything the professor said.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I have a lot on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Me too, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My lost memory and the events occurring right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there something connecting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, the nameless Pharaoh's power cannot be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.55,0:10:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the God Cards are right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.81,0:10:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an enormous power\N within these cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This power must not be wasted on something as trivial as the nameless Pharaoh's lost memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These shall act as the keys required to open the Forbidden Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When these cards\N are placed as offerings...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the sealed gate will open...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And our god will revive once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.04,0:11:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our supreme God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We grant upon you the power of the three gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And accepting this powerful offering, grant us your blessing and open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, the Forbidden Gate has been opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.98,0:11:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's asking us for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.48,0:12:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.85,0:12:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could they be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriboh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.31,0:12:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing in this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriboh's trying to guide us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow him, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuriboh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a place like this in my room...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.52,0:13:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chosen Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You finally came!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Magician Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were the one calling us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now both our world and your world, Master's, is on the verge of being destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our world and your world coincide with one another through different dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our world was created by your world's Thought Energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, our world depends upon your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both worlds rely upon each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.44,0:15:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But something is causing the balance between both worlds to collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Dark Sun has taken over our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of our companions are being devoured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a way to save our world and your world?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the three guardians of the Duel Monsters World, the Legendary Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They exhausted all of their power in their last battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're now sleeping here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did they get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one here even remembers their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.86,0:16:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.10,0:16:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that is left behind of these dragons is a prophecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prophecy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When our world and our Master's world is on the verge of collapse,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,only the True Duelists\N will awaken us dragons."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the True Duelists...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you can cure these dragons, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ice is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My other self...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timaeus!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.15,0:17:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monocle of Timaeus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has the power to bring out the hidden strength of all other Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:17:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.65,0:17:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That power...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An aurora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.76,0:18:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.16,0:18:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something came out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.59,0:19:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.01,0:19:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become the offering\N for our God's revival!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.08,0:19:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.95,0:19:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.22,0:19:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't just a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend us your power, Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that dragon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Timaeus...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The portal to your world has been closed once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the evil power has escaped somewhere in your world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our companions are also still captured...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.51,0:21:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Evil God will surely revive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master! Defeat that Evil God!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, both of our worlds will enter a path of doom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our inherited power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:22:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.10,0:22:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.58,0:22:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.86,0:22:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.76,0:22:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.43,0:23:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.94,0:23:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That giant eye monster appeared last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the monster Professor Hopkins mentioned that will destroy the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi received the power of the Legendary Dragon from the Duel Monsters World.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going on, but whatever it is, it can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment, Yugi gets a video.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.50,0:23:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sender is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.80,0:23:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.43,0:23:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Invitation From Pegasus"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
